biosecLogger.core

Class UserTemplate

  • java.lang.Object
    • biosecLogger.core.UserTemplate
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ExUserTemplate

    public class UserTemplate
extends java.lang.Object
    UserTemplate class creates formatted data from raw logged data. Formatted data are used to evaluate with sample.
    Author:
    Stefan Smihla
